CHANGELOG.md export-ignore
phpunit.xml.dist export-ignore
/tests export-ignore
/docs export-ignore
/.github export-ignore

# Mark files as binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
